# API说明文档

## 根部API https://fingerprint.com

### 登录
### /tglogin
- Method: POST
- Request: 【body】
```json
{
    "initData": "Telegram.WebApp.initData", //Telegram 用户数据
    "fingerprint": "详情 ： https://demo.fingerprint.com/" //指纹
}
```
- Response:
```json
{
    "token": "xxxxxx",
    "code": "0正常"
}
```


### 开始游戏
#### /startgame 
- Method: POST
- Request: 【body】
```json
{
    "token": "/tglogin 返回的token",
    "userid": 12345678
}
```
### 拾取奖励
#### /pickup 
- Method: POST
- Request: 【body】
```json
{
    "token": "/tglogin 返回的token",
    "userid": 12345678
}
```

### 签到界面初始化
#### /sign 
- Method: POST
- Request: 【body】
```json
{
    "token": "/tglogin 返回的token",
    "userid": 12345678
}
```
### 签到动作
#### /singnin 
- Method: POST
- Request: 【body】
```json
{
    "token": "/tglogin 返回的token",
    "userid": 12345678
}
```
